pi-server.py recieves events and logs them to a file

In /home/play run 

./pi-server.py -d 

To see the options 

./py-server --help
---------------------------

new_geo_cosmic_pi.py is the client that talks to the Arduino 
and sends events over UDP to the server

----------------------------

geo_cosmic_pi.cc is the arduino code.
N.B. This requires some modifications in the addafruit libraries
before it can be compiled

----------------------------


